commit.message: remove member '__unused' from struct
configure: use pkg-config for libev

pingu_route: copy source address over when cloning routes

pingu_route_clone did not copy src field. This would have resulted in routes
with an explicit source address "losing" the source address when their gateway
went down and came back up.

pingu_route: record correct device for each route

pingu_route_clone did not copy dev_index field. This resulted in routes being
added back with the wrong device when a gateway went down and came back up.
(Particularly when 2 interfaces both had the same default gateway address.)
